ReqConnect AppMode.WAN_APPAppMode.LOCAL_APPAppMode.LAN_APP Note <p>The robot connects to the internet via 4G or wifi. <code>robotId</code> is a required field.</p> TypeScript<pre><code>// Initialize robot operation instance
...
this.axRobot = new AXRobot(
    "&lt;appId&gt;", 
    "&lt;appSecret&gt;",
    AppMode.WAN_APP) // dev

try {
    let isOk = await this.axRobot.init()
    //console.log(isOk)
    if (isOk === true) {
        let res = await this.axRobot.connectRobot({
            robotId: '81822013xxxx', // Robot SN
        })
    }
} catch (e) {
    console.log(e)
}
</code></pre> Note <p>The upper computer connects to the robot chassis via a wired connection.</p> TypeScript<pre><code>// Initialize robot operation instance
